<p-change/>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5104007001" page = "2">
<title>
Scan Tool Data Definitions:
</title>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007002">
<title>
Input Shaft Revolution (rpm)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates input shaft speed detected by input shaft speed sensor.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007003">
<title>
Output Shaft Revolution (rpm)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates output shaft speed detected by output shaft speed sensor.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007004">
<title>
Battery Voltage (V)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates battery positive voltage inputted through A/T relay to TCM.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007005">
<title>
ATF Temperature (&#176;C, &#176;F)
</title>
<ptxt>
ATF temperature detected by signal from ATF temperature sensor installed on valve body.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007006">
<title>
Pressure Control Sol (Pressure Control Solenoid Valve Control Duty Ratio, %)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates control duty ratio of pressure control solenoid valve controlled by TCM.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007007">
<title>
TCC Solenoid Duty (TCC Solenoid Valve Control Duty Ratio, %)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates control duty ratio of TCC solenoid valve controlled by TCM.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007008">
<title>
Vehicle Speed (km/h/MPH)
</title>
<ptxt>
Vehicle speed computed by reference pulse signals coming from vehicle speed sensor on transaxle case.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007009">
<title>
Gear Position (1st, P/N, R)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates current gear position controlled by TCM based on transmission range sensor, vehicle speed (i.e. output shaft speed sensor signal) and throttle opening information received from ECM.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007010">
<title>
Slip RPM (rpm)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates slipping rotation in the torque converter (difference between input shaft speed and engine speed)
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007011">
<title>
Throttle Position (%)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates throttle position information received from ECM.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007012">
<title>
Accel Actual Position (%)
</title>
<ptxt>
Accelerator pedal opening ratio detected by signal on CAN communication line fed from ECM.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007013">
<title>
Engine Speed (rpm)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates engine speed information received from ECM.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007014">
<title>
ECT (Engine Coolant Temperature, &#176;C, &#176;F)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates engine coolant temperature information received from ECM.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007015">
<title>
Transaxle Range (P, R, N, D, 2, L)
</title>
<ptxt>
Transaxle range detected by signal fed from transmission range sensor.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007016">
<title>
3 Position (O/D Off) SW (ON / OFF)
</title>
<ptxt>
Inputted signal from O/D off switch in select lever assembly.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
ON: O/D off switch pushed
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
OFF: O/D off switch released
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007017">
<title>
Shift Solenoid A (Command, ON/OFF)
</title>
<ptxt>
ON: ON command being outputted to shift solenoid valve “A”
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
OFF: ON command not being outputted to shift solenoid valve “A”
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007018">
<title>
Shift Solenoid B (Command, ON/OFF)
</title>
<ptxt>
ON: ON command being outputted to shift solenoid valve “B”
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
OFF: ON command not being outputted to shift solenoid valve “B”
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007019">
<title>
Timing Solenoid (Command, ON/OFF)
</title>
<ptxt>
ON: ON command being outputted to timing solenoid valve
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
OFF: ON command not being outputted to timing solenoid valve
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007020">
<title>
Shift Solenoid A (Monitor, ON/OFF)
</title>
<ptxt>
ON: Electricity being passed to shift solenoid valve “A”
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
OFF: Electricity not being passed to shift solenoid valve “A”
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007021">
<title>
Shift Solenoid B (Monitor, ON/OFF)
</title>
<ptxt>
ON: Electricity being passed to shift solenoid valve “B”
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
OFF: Electricity not being passed to shift solenoid valve “B”
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007022">
<title>
Timing Solenoid (Monitor, ON/OFF)
</title>
<ptxt>
ON: Electricity being passed to timing solenoid valve
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
OFF: Electricity not being passed to timing solenoid valve
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007023">
<title>
Air Conditioner Signal (ON/OFF)
</title>
<ptxt>
ON: Signal which inform that air conditioner compressor is turned ON.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
OFF: Signal which inform that air conditioner compressor is not turned ON.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007024">
<title>
Brake Switch (ON/OFF)
</title>
<ptxt>
Inputted signal from brake light switch on pedal bracket.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
ON: Brake pedal depressed
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
OFF: Brake pedal released
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENAP70B5104007025">
<title>
MIL Request (ON/OFF)
</title>
<ptxt>
ON: Signal which TCM requires combination meter to turn on malfunction indicator lamp.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
OFF: Signal which TCM does not require combination meter to turn on malfunction indicator lamp.
</ptxt>
</topic>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
